column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: STIMOROL GUM SPEARMINT, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210059338
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: sweeteners ( xylitol, isomalt, sorbitol, maltitol syrup, acesulfame K, sucralose), gum base, flavourings, stabilisier (E414), emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), colours ( E171, E100, E133). Excessive consumption may produce laxative effects. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/26/2016
